Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade in a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:41.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:17.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.59,0:01:38.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He got me…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.75,0:01:41.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zabimaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:45.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:48.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:51.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My body feels heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:54.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My legs…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.46,0:01:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:01:58.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My arms…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.48,0:02:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,won't rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.92,0:02:04.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have I lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:14.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:55.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When she left, I was the one\Nwho didn't go after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:08.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“Hanging Dog,” the 78th district\Nin South Rukongai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.14,0:03:11.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the east, west, north and south,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:14.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukongai has districts numbered\Nfrom one to eighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:17.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,District One has the\Nhighest standard of living,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:21.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and a district like 78\Nwas the lowest of the low.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:25.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And we were kids who\Nlived in such a lowly town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:33.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We never knew what would happen to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,if there was even the slightest provocation\Nof the grown-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.08,0:03:38.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit staring like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:39.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:44.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still…we did anything\Nwe could to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.44,0:03:48.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:01.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now's our chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:05.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yay!\N– It's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:09.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:13.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, you brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:18.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can beg forgiveness,\Nbut I won't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.36,0:04:21.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, this is bad! He's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:23.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.17,0:04:26.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Taking me lightly, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:30.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:33.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We hated this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:39.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:54.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:05:00.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up! Do you want others to\Ncome after you for the water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:05.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.77,0:05:10.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We met…in a town like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:24.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I divided up the snacks we got.\NThis is your share.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.20,0:05:27.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Confetti candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Confetti candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:39.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you even know that?\NIt's sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:42.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:47.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:49.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:58.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you? You don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.14,0:06:00.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't got an ounce of\Nspiritual energy anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.23,0:06:04.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you have water, you don't get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a crybaby! Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:11.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, I said! What a racket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:12.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:13.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.87,0:06:17.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not get hungry? We're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:20.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!\NYou're just a newbie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:28.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We may not get hungry.\NBut we can taste! We can smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.34,0:06:32.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Happiness is to be shared\Namong everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.07,0:06:36.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like those dirty adults!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:49.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry anymore.\NHere, you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:58.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even she must've been\Nreluctant to give it away…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:06:59.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia was different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:14.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She had a big attitude,\Nand she spoke like a man…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:16.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.52,0:07:20.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.69,0:07:26.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're the weird one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.01,0:07:37.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you laughing at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:43.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But whatever she did, there was\Nan aura of refinement around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.63,0:08:04.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Look at this rickshaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:17.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's so shiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can see yourself! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's something, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:28.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is going to become\NMr. Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to be the pride of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.59,0:08:32.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:37.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In order to become a Soul Reaper,\Nyou've gotta have a ton of spiritual energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that means we're totally out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.17,0:08:43.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Get your dirty hands off that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.86,0:08:53.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There he comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.50,0:08:56.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.77,0:08:59.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:21.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kids hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err…no, we're not hungry…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:29.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling hungry in this world where\Nyou're not supposed to get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was confused about it at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:36.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a reality that you have to accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think your body felt\Nmy Spiritual Pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:42.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,which used up your\Nown energy instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here, eat these.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No need to hesitate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:53.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:10.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Renji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.19,0:10:14.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you're gonna become\Na real Soul Reaper one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:20.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:21.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's way bigger than Renji's!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.72,0:10:22.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:28.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia and Renji should both\Nbecome Soul Reapers! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:30.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will always be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stay here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:36.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:39.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:42.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be together forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:45.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Together!\N– Together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:53.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With or without spiritual energy,\Nit didn't matter one bit back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:58.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But, even though she lived in the dregs,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:00.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,she always shined.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, it's coming your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:07.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:15.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you keep running around\Nlike that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:21.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the other fish will get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:29.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:42.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:52.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! How do you like my talent, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.39,0:11:54.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys,\Nget the fire ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you standing around for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What did you do that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:21.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Before we realized it,\Nwe were together, always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.56,0:12:24.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We were a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:34.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…this was still a dirty town\Nwith dirty people living dirty lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:37.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The grown-ups were either\Nthieves or murderers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The kids were all delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:43.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone around us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.57,0:12:46.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:51.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to get out of this life…\Nthere was just one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:53.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:12:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's become Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:04.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If we become Soul Reapers,\Nwe can live in Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:11.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's a nice place\Nto live inside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:20.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Each of us came here all alone,\Nsearching for a family, and came together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:27.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But this town was just too cruel\Nfor kids like us to survive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years had passed since….\NRukia had become our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:40.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of our friends were all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's become Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:59.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shortly after that, we both entered\Nthe Soul Reaper Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:03.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And our school life began,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:05.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,among the spoiled brats\Nof the noble families.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.10,0:14:06.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.14,0:14:09.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I know that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me solve it, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.14,0:14:15.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like your spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But in order for you to write\Non this blackboard,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.07,0:14:22.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,the other students around you would\Nhave to stand up to let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.74,0:14:24.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll do it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:28.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has no common sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.16,0:14:31.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's from District 78 of Rukongai,\Nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:35.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why's he in such a rush\Nto prove himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:38.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He really is vulgar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.20,0:14:39.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:42.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's move on to\Nthe next problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:51.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:56.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…shucks!\NI can't waste time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:00.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Because unlike you,\NI'm in a special promotion class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:02.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:06.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I like it when you raise\Nyour hands eagerly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.28,0:15:14.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So…so keep showing\Nthat enthusiasm. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.62,0:15:16.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.24,0:15:27.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Most of the students here\Ncome from nobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They can't understand the feelings of\Nthose who've led our kind of existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:38.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:43.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even after we left Rukongai\Nand came to this Academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there was a huge gap\Nbetween them and us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:51.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I swore to myself that\NI’d make them eat their words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:53.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.23,0:15:59.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:13.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia! You've gotta hear this!\NI passed the Second Exam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now if I pass the next one, I…{\N235	02:31:22:11	02:31:23:03}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kenseikan…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:28.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nobles?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:33.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… it seems we've been interrupted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:40.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, we will await\Na favorable answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:55.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This…amazing Spiritual Pressure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even look into his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:17.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…Hey Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that seemed pretty intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.99,0:17:28.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– The Kuchiki family…\N– Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,wants me as their adopted daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.01,0:17:37.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They'll let me graduate right away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:43.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and make arrangements to put me\Ninto one of the 13 Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.41,0:17:48.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:53.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:56.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Kuchiki Family is\Na powerful noble family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:58.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:18:02.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you're adopted by a family like that,\Nyou'll live in luxury!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:05.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what you eat as a noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:08.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Man! I'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:12.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that…\NYou can graduate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I'm so jealous,\NI could throw up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's great! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I'm speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:30.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.76,0:18:41.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia finally found a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:45.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t interfere, I mustn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.74,0:18:49.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I kept telling myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:07.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think back…\NI may've just been scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.55,0:19:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I'm a stray dog down\Nto my bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.06,0:19:18.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:29.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I only bark at the stars…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:32.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the guts to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:48.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault that Rukia was imprisoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:52.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I thought about it,\Nmy blood boiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.12,0:19:55.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But that wasn't it…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I didn't stop Rukia…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:04.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That time, I…I didn't tell Rukia to\Ngo to the Kuchiki Family
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:07.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so she'd end up being\Na condemned criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:11.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought Rukia would find happiness…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I truly believed that…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:20.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to surpass Captain Kuchiki…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.59,0:20:25.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From that day, ever since…\NI've pursued him…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.15,0:20:27.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Every day I trained like mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:33.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I still haven't been able\Nto beat him, not once.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:35.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:39.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Getting Rukia back with strength…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.29,0:20:42.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was something I couldn't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.47,0:20:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki… I'm swallowing my shame\Nand asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:52.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Save…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:58.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Save…Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:12.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:17.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I shall put that unreachable fang\Nin flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:20.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that I need not look at that star.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:24.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that this throat will not be torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:27.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:42.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up into the night sky\Nand saw a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.07,0:21:49.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now,\Nbut I can't fly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:56.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:22:01.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would fly across the sky… I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:09.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would circle the skies and shine over you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:13.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this instantaneous light\Nthat will definitely reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:21.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.49,0:22:25.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll always stay close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:27.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:36.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am the new century's\Ncharismatic medium, Don Kanonji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:38.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This positively reeks of bad things!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:42.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What about the fight?\N– This definitely smells like bad spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.12,0:22:45.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– And my injury?\N– Good kids nationwide, you just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.31,0:22:48.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Bohahahaha!\N– What's going on?!